## ðŸ’¡ PRO TIPS

**Context Window Management**:
- Load only 2-3 files at a time
- Start with Quick Wins + Assessment
- Swap files as you move between phases
- Keep Master Checklist always loaded

**Efficient Referencing**:
- Use exact file names in prompts
- Cite specific sections: "Reference 11-upwork-templates.md, Headline section"
- Copy templates directly - don't rewrite from scratch

**Progress Tracking**:
- Update Master Checklist every 4 hours
- Log completed tasks in real-time
- Track blockers immediately when they occur
- Note time/budget deviations

**Emergency Protocol**:
- If lost: Return to 00-MASTER-CHECKLIST.md
- If blocked: Check 08-contingency-protocols.md
- If behind: Reference contingency decision trees
- If unsure: Check 07-quick-wins.md for priorities

